{"tid":852860,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過荃灣間大井町日式放題？質素如何？","createTime":"2018-10-08T07:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T01:18:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4947186173610ddacb458a9ffeeb201699de75","tid":852860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"好似好好食"},{"pid":"90d2858d15c13dbb06d47374258354b2f525fcb7","tid":852860,"uid":172075,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"1c416f764cdbd27135c316815875a384fcceff28","tid":852860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"90d2858d15c13dbb06d47374258354b2f525fcb7","tid":852860,"uid":172075,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:57:43.000Z","msg":"真？你食過？"},{"pid":"baf2baad9a97d6369c414e9128647bcf79449492","tid":852860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"無人知？"},{"pid":"d955fd57aac0f94e9c02ee3c1538c5d94ea06131","tid":852860,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"去過。單係荃灣黎講算幾好選擇"},{"pid":"9aa5abb386501b13f5f4de079badc876add6d577","tid":852860,"uid":38744,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾中嘅垃圾，請我都唔撚會去食<br />\n<br />\n咁多年黎<br />\n大大話話食過數十間放題<br />\n多數都唔會記得係咩名<br />\n因為多數都係中規中距，唔會有咩驚喜<br />\n<br />\n但呢間垃圾嘅程度係我一世都會記得叫咩名<br />\n好彩之前係fd請我食，唔洗錢<br />\n不過真係再請我都唔撚會去食<br />\n<br />\n冇樣野好食<br />\n成間野最好食係燒汁雞串呀屌你老母！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/08/170458_4071bf418785cc284160d0dde736f320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2F170458_4071bf418785cc284160d0dde736f320.jpg&h=7a46c0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係就咁放落微波爐到叮就食得嘅呢隻呀屌你<br />\n<br />\n巴打<br />\n千其唔好去"},{"pid":"9ae3d05ff27a8694c27701208eff0181aa7ba790","tid":852860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"d955fd57aac0f94e9c02ee3c1538c5d94ea06131","tid":852860,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"去過。單係荃灣黎講算幾好選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"聽你咁講，好似真係值得去喎"},{"pid":"e560b45c57a9dd623dac1c198e4edf8a60162d71","tid":852860,"uid":28612,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"屌你樓主打手味濃撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e917913515ce58c42b44cf0e9c0f4f86ba780c57","tid":852860,"uid":100099,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"呢間野係我食過最深刻既一次放題<br />\n因為係冇一樣係好食<br />\n只係有好難食，好撚難食，冇咁難食3個 level<br />\n衰過兆萬既是但一間<br />\n刺身未解晒凍<br />\n壽司完全冇鮮味唔知食緊乜<br />\n炸野燒物一早炸定燒定加熱少少就出<br />\n牛柳粒咬唔爛<br />\n天婦羅炸漿厚過 m巾<br />\n甜品全部都係伏到仆街<br />\n布丁係化學劑味，口感似痰<br />\n泡芙同撻類係淋到仆街<br />\n成餐最好食係1人1杯既dreyer's<br />\n呢間野佢免費我都唔會再試"},{"pid":"271e9f01d65e5b94c953bebeee72b33d294209a5","tid":852860,"uid":6251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:54:13.000Z","msg":"荃灣黎講漁屋好過啦"},{"pid":"6ad2573d439afa329189e81b9b444b82d8b64a7f","tid":852860,"uid":125207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"剛開張果期都仲算可以 起碼燒物都真係燒出黎<br />\n上個月朋友生日去左食 連隻燒雞翼都變左煎雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他野更加係垃圾 學上面講 串叮雞可能已然係最好食果樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf5bfc64467fba74ed680bd819fb5453d5458dc","tid":852860,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"6ad2573d439afa329189e81b9b444b82d8b64a7f","tid":852860,"uid":125207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"剛開張果期都仲算可以 起碼燒物都真係燒出黎<br />\n上個月朋友生日去左食 連隻燒雞